<title>ạllh bytklm</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 ạlqrạr- ạllh bytklm ly wlyk .. ạllh byklm kl ạlnạs
 bṣwt wṣwrẗ mn ḥwạlyk .. ql lh yʿṭyk qlb ḥsạs
 1- (ạllh bytklm wsṭ ạlnạr .. bạlṣmt byʿln ạ̉w bạlṣwt
 bhdyr ạlạ̉mwạj ạlʿạṣf .. bṣyạḥ ạldyk wf bṭn ạlḥwt)2
 (ḥty̱ ạlqbr ykẖbr lmạ)2 .. yw̉mr bḥyạẗ mn qlb ạlmwt
 2- (ạllh bytklm fy ẓrwfy .. wf qlb ạlḥạjẗ wạlạ̉ʿwạz
 bṭrq ṭbyʿyẗ bytklm .. wạ̹n sẖạʾ ytklm bạlạ̹ʿjạz)2
 (ạlfạhm ylms yd ạllh)2 .. wạljạhl yḥsbhạ ạ̉lgẖạz
 3- (ạllh byqwl lkn qlby .. mḥtạj ytʿlm kyf ysmʿ
 tnṭfy ạ̉nwạr ạlạ̉rḍyạt .. wạrfʿ ʿyny ʿlyh wạtṭlʿ)2
 (ạ̉smʿ ṣwth wạsẖbʿ mnh)2 .. wmjdh wnwrh fy hysṭʿ</lyrics>
</song>